headline: What Recent AI Device News Means for HP Stock in 2025
summary: Trying to decide what to do with HP stock right now? You are not alone. After all, the shares have had quite a ride this year, bouncing back 7.5% in just the last week. That quick gain stands in contrast to slower action earlier in the year, and even with a tougher stretch (down 12.1% so far in 2024), HP remains up an impressive 74.0% over the last five years. The moves show that investors are starting to weigh new realities for the company and may be reassessing HP’s risk and growth profile...

headline: Fed Chair Powell hints at rate cuts, Fastenal reports Q3 earnings
summary: Yahoo Finance anchor Josh Lipton tracks Tuesday's top moving stocks and biggest market stories in this Market Minute. Federal Reserve Chair Jerome Powell spoke at the National Association for Business Economics (NABE) in Philadelphia, making remarks suggesting that further rate cuts are in the cards at the Fed's October meeting. Fastenal (FAST) reported third quarter results that beat Wall Street estimates. HP Inc. (HPQ) was upgraded to Buy from Hold by HSBC analysts. Stay up to date on the latest market action, minute-by-minute, with Yahoo Finance's Market Minute.
